    "The proposed work tries to find the significance of the identified variables by determining the scale for which the project may achieve the highest probability of success.",
    "This will help the software practitioners to focus more on the important aspects of the 6G-SQC project for its effective execution.",
    "We have used Genetic Algorithms (GA) to maximize the project success probability while minimizing the associated cost to achieve this objective.",
    "(GA will generate states of factors and calculate success probability with the help of predictive models.",
    "It will also try to balance success probability and cost to identify affordable scales of factors."
